Package de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.engine.process.interleaving

Class AbstractInterleavingPhaseManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.engine.process.interleaving.AbstractInterleavingPhaseManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PhaseManager
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultGeneratingInterleavingPhaseManager, DefaultTestingInterleavingPhaseManager
    public abstract class AbstractInterleavingPhaseManager
extends Object
implements PhaseManager
    Abstract class implementing the PhaseManager Interface for Interleaving CT. It provides general functionality and fields used by all sub-classes.

    Manages a ResultCache to execute every test input exactly once. If a test input has been executed before, the PhaseManager loads the result from the cache instead of executing the ExecutionPhase.
